{"tid":947155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旅行慘死】兩女遊客陳屍摩洛哥山區 一遭斬首一遭割喉","createTime":"2018-12-19T05:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T09:17:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21559486d77d94a223cdd08de99e19ca68ea9c6d","tid":947155,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"兩名北歐女遊客結伴到摩洛哥登山，周一卻被發現陳屍在山區旅遊勝地，其中一人被斬首，另一人被割喉。摩洛哥經濟依賴旅遊業，兇殺案發生後當局立即加強安全措施，目前已拘捕一名疑犯，相信有多於一人犯案。<br />\n死者為24歲丹麥人耶斯佩森（Louisa Vesterager Jespersen）及28歲挪威女子尤蘭（Maren Ueland），兩人打算登上北非最高峯圖什凱山（Toubkal），在山腳附近偏遠山村伊姆利爾（Imlil）外近10公里的山區中共用一個帳篷過夜。她們的屍體被發現時，一人在帳篷內，另一人在帳篷旁邊，頸部均有傷痕，一人被斬首，另一人被割喉。<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》報道，事發後挪威已派出一名警員抵達現場，疑犯為三名流浪漢。摩洛哥內政部後來表示，警方在伊姆利爾以北65公里的馬拉喀什（Marrakesh）拘捕一名疑犯，當局正追緝其他與案有關的疑犯。<br />\n根據傳媒報道，兩名受害人都在挪威南部的泰勒馬克大學學院（Telemark University College）就讀，相約聖誕節假在高阿特拉斯山脈（High Atlas）行山。耶斯佩森的媽媽透露愛女慘被割喉，又指家人曾警告她，稱摩洛哥「局勢混亂」，曾要她不要去摩洛哥。尤蘭的媽媽亦指，兩女其實也擔心安全問題，「她們在出發前採取了所有預防措施」。<br />\n伊姆利爾山村的出事現場是登上圖什凱山的起點，兇案發生後，當局已加強當地保安，禁止行山活動，一名導遊表示：「（兇殺案）對該地區有負面影響，毫無疑問會有人取消預約。」案件也引起登山會「卡薩布蘭卡法國高山俱樂部」的憂慮，該會主要在高阿特拉斯山脈組織登山活動，登山會工作人員正在查看是否有女性單獨登山。<br />\n摩洛哥經濟多年來停滯不前，近年旅遊業終於有起色，去年有1,135萬人次入境，首次突破1,100萬人次大關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545184928_30de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545184928_30de.jpg&h=ab6515f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545185130_af2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545185130_af2c.jpg&h=5e77d96a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545185130_9c9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545185130_9c9a.jpg&h=ba53b7ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181219/59046342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046342&d=jwGvS68r2ymNx0b%2BIwoJjeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=e702e5e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046342&h=c98bec92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181219/59046342</a>"},{"pid":"6b300a5bc2365434589e3425fafa3275f5de09ee","tid":947155,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"咁靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天妒紅顏<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e09e696fa5d3dee191d440895ac809ee8ec85f1","tid":947155,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"咁都食得落"},{"pid":"1b537b83105beb64efd242585193fe53a5c87303","tid":947155,"uid":35648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"玩咩玩到斬首<br />\n又係隊野隊到有幻覺？"},{"pid":"47b3a4c07a8c747fc07bdd50defb806de3c84d8a","tid":947155,"uid":39320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"隻狗咁撚大隻"},{"pid":"7aee259b3a909cff2f4dac517f459e68eab836b1","tid":947155,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"巴拿馬嗰單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538e159c0a2dda615e6a4f3412dd4d6a9f53853b","tid":947155,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aee259b3a909cff2f4dac517f459e68eab836b1","tid":947155,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"巴拿馬嗰單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:17:53.000Z","